<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #4caf50;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .details {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        padding-top: 20px;
      }
      .details p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #999999;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #4caf50;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
      <p>Dear Customer,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for your purchase! Your order for the following course has
        been successfully placed:
      </p>
      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
        <p><strong>Price:</strong> $<%= price %></p>
        <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= _id %></p>
      </div>
      <p>
        We hope you enjoy your learning experience. If you have any questions,
        feel free to contact our support team.
      </p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Course Team</p>
        <p><a href="https://example.com">Visit our website</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
